cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and robotics, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) sub-categories. The use of deep learning techniques also suggests that it could belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of descriptors and matching, which are common techniques in computer vision and could suggest the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category. Finally, the use of point clouds could suggest the cs.GR (Graphics) sub-category.
